law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 434, sec. 15, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 398, sec. 9, effective June 17, 1978. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 3187d, 3187g.
